title: About
permalink: /about/
---

{% from "components/sectionhead.njk" import sectionhead %}

<section>
  <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-5">
    {{ sectionhead("About" ) }}

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 mx-auto max-w-4xl mt-16">
   <h2 class="font-bold text-3xl text-gray-800">
        Our History
      </h2>
<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-500">Refresh DC is organized by a volunteer board pulling from events, education, and special projects, each bringing different backgrounds and skills to the table. Interested in volunteering? Let us know.</p>
<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-500">Refresh DC is for people building the web: developers, designers, strategists, writers, entrepreneurs, and anyone working at the intersection of creativity and technology in the Washington DC area. It&#39;s a place to share what you&#39;re working on, learn from people doing the same, and find your people in an industry too big for any one person to know it all.</p>
<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-500">It&#39;s been over 20 years now, and that&#39;s still what we do best. Whether it&#39;s a technical talk, a hands on workshop, an education initiative, or just good conversation over drinks, Refresh DC remains a place where DC&#39;s creative and tech communities can discover new ideas, connect with peers, and refresh.</p>
      <h2 class="font-bold text-3xl text-gray-800">
         Team
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-500">
        Refresh DC is organized by a volunteer board pulling from events, education, and special projects, each bringing different backgrounds and skills to the table. Interested in volunteering? Let us know.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 mx-auto max-w-4xl mt-12">
      {% set publishedTeam = collections.team | published | sortByLastName %}
      {% for member in publishedTeam %}
        <div class="group">
          <div class="w-full aspect-square">
            <img
              src="{{ member.data.avatar.src }}"
              alt="{{ member.data.avatar.alt }}"
              width="400"
              height="400"
              class="w-full rounded-md transition group-hover:-translate-y-1 group-hover:shadow-xl bg-white object-cover object-center aspect-square"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-lg text-gray-800">{{ member.data.name }}</h2>
            <h3 class="text-sm text-slate-500">{{ member.data.title }}</h3>
            {% if member.data.linkedin %}
              <a href="{{ member.data.linkedin }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block mt-2 text-slate-400 hover:text-rf-blue transition">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 01-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 112.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/>
                </svg>
              </a>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
